---
title: Sweet Chilli & Oyster Pork with Garlic Rice, Pickled Cucumber & Peanuts
description: There have been many combos of pork and rice with something nice for years and years, but have you ever tasted a
combo of sweet chilli and oyster sauce, glazed on pork? If not and even if you have, we recommend digging into this one.
Crunchy peanuts and a pickled cucumber add that ‘something nice’ we mentioned. It’s another recipe for the ages.

